snippet: Australia withdrew from two friendly matches that were to be part of the United States women’s national team’s World Cup victory tour, but U.S. Soccer said the games would go on with Haiti as a replacement opponent.
abstract: Australian women’s soccer team, which is in labor dispute with country’s soccer federation, cancels two upcoming exhibition matches that were part of United States women's team's World Cup victory tour.
lead_paragraph: Australia withdrew from two friendly matches that were to be part of the United States women’s national team’s World Cup victory tour, but U.S. Soccer said the games would go on with Haiti as a replacement opponent.
